<h1>Welcome, <%= current_user.name %>.</h1>
<p><%= @shop.text %></p>
<p>The last chosen present is the one that will be shipped.</p>
<p>Your choice of present can be changed up to and including <em><%= l(@shop.closes_on) %></em>.</p>
<p>You will still be able to log in and view your final choice of present after the shop has closed.</p>
<% if current_user.orders.count > 0 %>
  <span class="choice">For your information, you have previously chosen <%= link_to current_user.orders.last.product.name, shop_product_path(@shop, current_user.orders.last.product) %>.</span>
<% end %>
